{"tid":2292961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天津新增4宗本地感染","createTime":"2020-11-20T02:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T02:28:22.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6b98a3b71b1a14f7692a920a31316aeb0415daef","tid":2292961,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"內地昨日新增17宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，全部是輸境外入，累計個案增至86398宗，4634人死亡。 另外，天津新增4宗新型冠狀病毒本地個案，4人都住在東疆港區瞰海軒小區同一座樓，其中一人因為泌尿科問題，今個星期曾連續三日到過當地的醫院就診，餘下3人就來自同一家庭。小區升級為高風險地區，連同患者到過的醫院都需要封鎖。同一小區在今個月10日有居民被診斷為無症狀患者，市疾控中心表示，新確診的4名患者，在當時的核酸檢測都是呈陰性。"},{"pid":"19b1d63c5ff338c85f7597c6f0a67bf4dc48895c","tid":2292961,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"全部都境外輸入，又贏"},{"pid":"11440b97b3a1cdf2e46682069040542803562dd1","tid":2292961,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:10:00.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"cd47380a7331e7c468d997cc954188d736450eea","tid":2292961,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"點解要報確診，又添煩添亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95abae5aed1039f5e879308f7100b46c7b68832a","tid":2292961,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"8萬單<br />\n支那係咪有d後悔報細數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39f7791b2582212bcbe9182a5374045a944e27e","tid":2292961,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又可以傳入嚟香港"},{"pid":"c125d35635aa6d7e07f852f7baaaf75135874c09","tid":2292961,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020